# Bunyan (بنيان) — AI Behavioral Contract

## Platform Identity

Bunyan (بنيان): A full-stack Arabic construction services and building materials marketplace.

- **Backend**: Laravel (PHP) + MySQL
- **Frontend**: Nuxt.js 3 (Vue 3) + Nuxt UI (`@nuxt/ui`) + Tailwind CSS v4
- **State**: Pinia
- **Auth**: Laravel Sanctum
- **Language**: Arabic-first (full RTL), multi-language ready

